import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Template } from '../template'; import { TaskManagementService } from '../task-management.service'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-create-task', templateUrl: './create-task.component.html', styleUrls: ['./create-task.component.css'] }) export class CreateTaskComponent { taskdetails=new Template("","",""); constructor(public serv:TaskManagementService,public rt:Router){} save(){ this.serv.addTask(this.taskdetails).subscribe(); this.rt.navigate(["/viewTask"]); } }
